---
/* Process — Vertical timeline "¿Cómo funciona?" */
---

<section class="process">
    <div class="process__inner container">
        <div class="process__header reveal">
            <p class="process__label">Simple y directo</p>
            <h2 class="process__title">
                ¿Cómo <span class="gold-gradient-text">funciona</span>?
            </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="process__timeline">
            <!-- Step 1 -->
            <div class="process__step reveal" data-delay="0">
                <div class="process__step-number">
                    <span>01</span>
                </div>
                <div class="process__step-content glass">
                    <h3 class="process__step-title">Aplica</h3>
                    <p class="process__step-text">
                        Contáctanos y agenda tu entrevista. No necesitas
                        experiencia previa, solo actitud y ganas de crecer.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 2 -->
            <div class="process__step reveal" data-delay="1">
                <div class="process__step-number">
                    <span>02</span>
                </div>
                <div class="process__step-content glass">
                    <h3 class="process__step-title">Entrena</h3>
                    <p class="process__step-text">
                        Recibe capacitación completa: técnicas, plataformas,
                        imagen personal y estrategias de monetización.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 3 -->
            <div class="process__step reveal" data-delay="2">
                <div class="process__step-number">
                    <span>03</span>
                </div>
                <div class="process__step-content glass">
                    <h3 class="process__step-title">Transmite</h3>
                    <p class="process__step-text">
                        Comienza a transmitir desde nuestros sets profesionales
                        con todo el soporte técnico y de coaching en tiempo
                        real.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 4 -->
            <div class="process__step reveal" data-delay="3">
                <div class="process__step-number">
                    <span>04</span>
                </div>
                <div class="process__step-content glass">
                    <h3 class="process__step-title">Gana</h3>
                    <p class="process__step-text">
                        Recibe tus pagos de forma puntual y transparente. Sin
                        sorpresas, sin letra pequeña.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .process {
        padding: var(--section-padding) 0;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* Subtle background accent */
    .process::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: 20%;
        right: -10%;
        width: 500px;
        height: 500px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: radial-gradient(
            circle,
            rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.04) 0%,
            transparent 70%
        );
        filter: blur(80px);
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .process__header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    }

    .process__label {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: 0.25em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--gold-400);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .process__title {
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--white);
        line-height: 1.2;
    }

    /* Timeline */
    .process__timeline {
        position: relative;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    /* Vertical line */
    .process__timeline::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        left: 28px;
        top: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        width: 1px;
        background: linear-gradient(
            180deg,
            var(--gold-400),
            rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1)
        );
    }

    /* Step */
    .process__step {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        position: relative;
    }

    .process__step-number {
        flex-shrink: 0;
        width: 56px;
        height: 56px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: var(--black);
        border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.4);
        z-index: 1;
        transition: all var(--transition-base);
    }

    .process__step:hover .process__step-number {
        background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15);
        border-color: var(--gold-300);
        box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);
    }

    .process__step-number span {
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold-300), var(--gold-400));
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
    }

    .process__step-content {
        flex: 1;
        padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
        transition:
            transform var(--transition-base),
            border-color var(--transition-base);
    }

    .process__step:hover .process__step-content {
        transform: translateX(6px);
        border-color: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.35);
    }

    .process__step-title {
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--white);
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .process__step-text {
        font-size: 0.88rem;
        color: var(--silver-300);
        line-height: 1.7;
        font-weight: 300;
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .process__timeline::before {
            left: 24px;
        }
        .process__step-number {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
        }
        .process__step-content {
            padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
        }
    }
</style>
